---
title: Bacon & Roasted Eggplant Fusilli with Crumbly Cheese & Basil
description: Add layers of flavour to fusilli with bacon and an array of rainbow veggies roasted in Mediterranean-inspired seasonings. Paired
with a rich tomato sauce and aromatic basil leaves, your finished dish will be transformed into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-roasted-eggplant-fusilli-197e17fa.jpg
